---
// src/pages/drive-thru/how-it-works.astro
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="How The Local Drive-Thru Works | Order Ahead & Pick Up Fast"
  description="Learn how The Local Drive-Thru works. Order ahead on Clover, drive up, and pick up your coffee, breakfast, or lunch without leaving your car. It's that simple."
  keywords="how to order drive thru, drive through ordering, order ahead Clover, drive thru coffee"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>How The Local Drive-Thru Works</h1>
      <p>It's Simple. It's Fast. It's Designed for People Like You.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/drive-thru">Drive-Thru</a></li>
        <li><span>How It Works</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="intro">
      <h2>The Drive-Thru Experience</h2>
      <p>
        You don't want to get out of your car. Your kids are in the backseat. It's raining. You're running late. Whatever your situation, we get it. That's why we're here. No parking hassles. No going inside. No waiting around. Just pull up, order (or pick up your pre-order), and go.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="process-section">
      <h2>5 Simple Steps</h2>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <h3>Order Ahead (Optional, But Smart)</h3>
          <p>
            Pull out your phone. Open Clover. Browse our menu. Customize your order however you want it. Hit submit. Boom. Done. Your order goes straight to the kitchen and we start making it immediately.
          </p>
          <p class="step-detail">
            <strong>Why do this?</strong> You pull up and your coffee's ready. No wait. No "five more minutes." It's there.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <h3>Drive Up to the Window</h3>
          <p>
            Head to 1171 TN-100 in Centerville. Pull around to the drive-thru window. No need to find a parking spot. No need to navigate through a building. Just roll up.
          </p>
          <p class="step-detail">
            <strong>Timing:</strong> If you ordered ahead, time it so you arrive 5-10 minutes after ordering. If you're ordering when you arrive, we'll have your food ready in about 3-5 minutes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <h3>Tell Us Your Order (Or We Hand It Over)</h3>
          <p>
            Already ordered on Clover? Just tell us your name. We'll hand you your order through the window. Haven't ordered yet? Tell us what you want and we'll get it ready for you right now.
          </p>
          <p class="step-detail">
            <strong>Pro tip:</strong> If you didn't order ahead and it's busy, don't worry. We're fast. Our limited menu means we know exactly what we're doing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <h3>Pay & Go</h3>
          <p>
            Hand us your card or cash. We process it right there at the window. Take your coffee, breakfast, or lunch. Stay in your car the whole time.
          </p>
          <p class="step-detail">
            <strong>No surprises:</strong> Prices on Clover match prices at the window. What you see is what you pay.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">5</div>
          <h3>Hit the Road</h3>
          <p>
            You've got your coffee. You've got your breakfast. You're already back in your car. Drive to work. Sit in your driveway. Go to the next thing. You're done here.
          </p>
          <p class="step-detail">
            <strong>That's it.</strong> No parking lot time. No going inside. In and out in minutes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="order-ahead-section">
      <h2>Order Ahead Guide</h2>
      <div class="guide-content">
        <div class="guide-block">
          <h3>Why Order Ahead?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Your order is ready when you arrive (no wait)</li>
            <li>You can customize exactly how you want it</li>
            <li>You can pay on your phone before you arrive</li>
            <li>Perfect for the morning commute rush</li>
            <li>Great for lunch breaks when you're busy</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-block">
          <h3>How to Order on Clover</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Go to <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-drivethru-centerville" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Clover ordering site</a></li>
            <li>Browse our menu (organized by category)</li>
            <li>Add items to your cart</li>
            <li>Customize each item (milk choice, size, extras)</li>
            <li>Choose pickup time (ASAP or schedule for later)</li>
            <li>Enter your name and payment</li>
            <li>Done. You'll get a confirmation</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="guide-block">
          <h3>Timing Your Order</h3>
          <p>
            Order while you're at home or at the office. Give us about 5-10 minutes to prepare. Then drive over and pick it up. If you're ordering on the road, let us know in the special instructions and we'll have it ready ASAP.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Common Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-items">
        <details class="faq-item" open>
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What if I don't order ahead?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>You can still order at the window. Just pull up and tell us what you want. We'll have it ready in 3-5 minutes. It's that simple.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>How long does it take if I order ahead?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>You'll pick up in about 5-10 minutes after you order. If you order ahead and come right away, it might be 2-3 minutes. We start making orders immediately when they come through.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I modify my order after I submit it on Clover?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you've just ordered, call us at (931) 729-4821 right away and we might be able to adjust it. Once we've started making it, changes are tougher. Best practice: double-check before you submit.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Do you take cash or cards only?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We take both. Cash or card at the window. If you order on Clover, you'll pay online, but you can still tip when you pick up if you'd like.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What's your busiest time?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Morning (7-8:30am) and lunch (12-1pm) are our busiest. If you're coming during those times, ordering ahead guarantees your order's ready and waiting. Other times, walkin orders are lightning fast.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I order for multiple people?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Absolutely. On Clover, you can add as many items as you want to one order. Just give us names at the window if there are multiple people in the car, or put special instructions on your order.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Do you have seating inside?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Nope. This is drive-thru only. No seating inside. You're eating in your car or taking it home. That's the whole pointâ€”convenient, fast, no need to get out.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What about dietary restrictions?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We can accommodate oat milk, almond milk, and other alternatives on most drinks. Tell us at the window or note it in Clover special instructions. For other dietary needs, call us at (931) 729-4821.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="location-info">
      <h2>Ready to Try It?</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Address:</strong> 1171 TN-100, Centerville, TN 37033<br />
        <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-4821">(931) 729-4821</a><br />
        <strong>Hours:</strong> Mon-Fri 5 AM - 6 PM | Sat 7 AM - 6 PM | Closed Sunday
      </p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-drivethru-centerville" class="cta-button">Order Now on Clover</a>
        <a href="/drive-thru" class="cta-button secondary">Back to Drive-Thru</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .step {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .step-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .step p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .step-detail {
    background: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.05);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  .guide-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .guide-block {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .guide-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .guide-block ul,
  .guide-block ol {
    margin-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .guide-block li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .guide-block a {
    color: #8b4513;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .guide-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    user-select: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    background: #efefef;
  }

  .toggle-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--white);
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .cta-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #8b4513;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #6b3410;
  }

  .cta-button.secondary {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .cta-button.secondary:hover {
    background: #ddd;
  }

  .location-info {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .location-info a {
    color: #8b4513;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .location-info a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .guide-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-group {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cta-button {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
